        text: 'The average score across all 25,000+ indexed tools is 29.6 out of 100. Anything above 70 is well above average. The top 10% start around 60. The top 1% start around 85. For production use, targeting servers with scores above 70 and individual issue health above 80% is a reasonable baseline.',
      },
